 Himera","\u003Cspan>M.T. Manni Piraino, «Alcune iscrizioni inedite dall’area sacra e dall’abitato di Himera», \u003Ci>Kokalos\u003C/i> 20 (1974): 265–71\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/6J3XUS7X",{"type":176,"bibl":177},"discussion",[16],{"editor":179,"principal":182,"contributors":185,"change":196},{"_":180,"ref":181},"Jonathan Prag","#JP",{"_":183,"ref":184},"Valentina Mignosa","#VM",[186,189,192],{"_":180,"xml:id":187,"ref":188},"JP","https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537",{"_":183,"xml:id":190,"ref":191},"VM","https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511",{"_":193,"xml:id":194,"ref":195},"Simona Stoyanova","SS","https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569",{"_":197,"when":198,"who":184},"Valentina Mignosa added metadata, text","2021-06-03","",{"n":93,"url":94,"height":95,"width":96,"desc":97,"surfaceType":98},[202],{"atLeast":203,"atMost":204},5,15,[206,207,208,209],"Arena, 1994, IGASM3","Dubois, 1989, IGDS1","Hansen, 1983-1989, Carmina epigraphica graeca saeculorum VIII-V a. Chr. n. [vol. I] and ... saeculi IV a. Chr. n. [II]. «Texte und Kommentare», 12, 15. ol. I, nos. 1-465; II, nos. 466-901.","Manni Piraino, 1974, Alcune iscrizioni inedite dall'area sacra e dall'abitato di Himera",[211,212,213,214],"KK5FQVHF","RWXNUFEX","PCVG9ND6","6J3XUS7X",[216,216,217,18,23,27,218,219,220,221,219,222,223,120],"isic020587",{"_":4},"himera","imera","italy","sicily","parco archeologico di himera e antiquarium","ancient greek",[],{"title":226,"body":227,"divs":228,"editions":255,"images":265,"handnote":271},"ISic020587. ISic020587","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">Ζε̄νὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐριγδούπ̣οιο κ̣όρε̄ι γλαυκο̄́πῑ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἀ͡θ\u003C/span>ε̄́νε̄ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">Θρίπυλος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> εὐξάμεν̣ος τε̄́νδ’ ἀνέθε̄κε̣ θεᾶι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">ΖΕ̄ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΡΙΓΔΟΥ.ΟΙΟ.ΟΡΕ̄ΙΓΛΑΥΚΟ̄ΠῙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Α͡Θ\u003C/span>Ε̄ΝΕ̄Ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">ΘΡΙΠΥΛΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΥΞΑΜΕ.ΟΣΤΕ̄ΝΔΑΝΕΘΕ̄Κ.ΘΕΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Arena (IGASM 3)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>To the bright-eyed Athena daughter of loud-thundering Zeus, Thripylos invoking dedicated this (kylix?) to the goddess.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Per Atena dagli occhi lucenti figlia di Zeus altitonante, Thripylos invocante ha dedicato questa (kylix?) alla dea.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Inscription incised in neat characters before firing on a base of a medium-sized vase. The inscription is a couplet of poetic inspiration whose first hemistich is the same as the beginning of v. 3 of the Homeric Hymn to Hera (Ζε̄νὸς ἐριγδούποιο). It is followed by another Homeric formula (γλαυκο̄́πῑ Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι) with a shortened form γλαυκο̄́πῑ rather than the recurring γλαυκῶπιν. The form κόρε̄ι has a vocalism that is attested in Euboea (cf. \u003Ca href=\"https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000747552\" target=\"_blank\">Bechtel 1921-1924\u003C/a>, 74). τε̄́νδ(ε) could refer to κύλικα but could also indicate something else. It is interesting to note that a clay and headless figurine of Athena was found near the vase (Manni Piraino 1974, p. 266).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1974 266, pl. XLII.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hansen 1983 392 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">8\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1994 45, pl. XIV.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1  5-15  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[229,232,235,238,241,243,246,249,252],{"id":230,"html":231},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">Ζε̄νὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐριγδούπ̣οιο κ̣όρε̄ι γλαυκο̄́πῑ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἀ͡θ\u003C/span>ε̄́νε̄ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">Θρίπυλος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> εὐξάμεν̣ος τε̄́νδ’ ἀνέθε̄κε̣ θεᾶι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">ΖΕ̄ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΡΙΓΔΟΥ.ΟΙΟ.ΟΡΕ̄ΙΓΛΑΥΚΟ̄ΠῙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Α͡Θ\u003C/span>Ε̄ΝΕ̄Ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">ΘΡΙΠΥΛΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΥΞΑΜΕ.ΟΣΤΕ̄ΝΔΑΝΕΘΕ̄Κ.ΘΕΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":233,"html":234},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":236,"html":237},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Arena (IGASM 3)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":239,"html":240},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>To the bright-eyed Athena daughter of loud-thundering Zeus, Thripylos invoking dedicated this (kylix?) to the goddess.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":239,"html":242},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Per Atena dagli occhi lucenti figlia di Zeus altitonante, Thripylos invocante ha dedicato questa (kylix?) alla dea.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":244,"html":245},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Inscription incised in neat characters before firing on a base of a medium-sized vase. The inscription is a couplet of poetic inspiration whose first hemistich is the same as the beginning of v. 3 of the Homeric Hymn to Hera (Ζε̄νὸς ἐριγδούποιο). It is followed by another Homeric formula (γλαυκο̄́πῑ Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι) with a shortened form γλαυκο̄́πῑ rather than the recurring γλαυκῶπιν. The form κόρε̄ι has a vocalism that is attested in Euboea (cf. \u003Ca href=\"https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000747552\" target=\"_blank\">Bechtel 1921-1924\u003C/a>, 74). τε̄́νδ(ε) could refer to κύλικα but could also indicate something else. It is interesting to note that a clay and headless figurine of Athena was found near the vase (Manni Piraino 1974, p. 266).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":247,"html":248},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1974 266, pl. XLII.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hansen 1983 392 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">8\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1994 45, pl. XIV.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":250,"html":251},"handnote","  Line 1  5-15  ",{"id":253,"html":254},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[256,258,261,262],{"html":257},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa",{"id":259,"lang":120,"html":260},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">Ζε̄νὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐριγδούπ̣οιο κ̣όρε̄ι γλαυκο̄́πῑ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἀ͡θ\u003C/span>ε̄́νε̄ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">Θρίπυλος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> εὐξάμεν̣ος τε̄́νδ’ ἀνέθε̄κε̣ θεᾶι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>",{"html":257},{"id":263,"lang":120,"html":264},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">ΖΕ̄ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΡΙΓΔΟΥ.ΟΙΟ.ΟΡΕ̄ΙΓΛΑΥΚΟ̄ΠῙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Α͡Θ\u003C/span>Ε̄ΝΕ̄Ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">ΘΡΙΠΥΛΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΥΞΑΜΕ.ΟΣΤΕ̄ΝΔΑΝΕΘΕ̄Κ.ΘΕΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>",[266,268],{"image":94,"thumb":267,"title":97},"ISic020587_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":269,"thumb":270,"title":97},"ISic020587.jpg","ISic020587-thumb.jpg",[],"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u00